---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Micro Loan - Small Ticket Loans up to ₹50,000 | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="#">Loans</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>Micro Loan</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Micro Loan</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Get instant micro loans from ₹3,000 to ₹50,000 for urgent expenses, bill payments, or short-term needs. 100% digital process with approval in minutes and disbursal within 1 hour. No collateral, no guarantor, minimal documentation.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i>
          <span>Loan Amount: ₹3K - ₹50K</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
          <span>Disbursal: Within 1 Hour</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-days"></i>
          <span>Tenure: 15 Days - 12 Months</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>What is a Micro Loan?</h2>
          <p>A micro loan is a small-ticket, short-tenure loan designed for immediate financial needs when you need a small amount quickly. Micro loans range from ₹3,000 to ₹50,000 with repayment tenures of 15 days to 12 months. They are fully digital — you can apply, get approved, and receive money in your bank account within 1 hour without any paperwork, branch visits, or lengthy verification processes. These loans bridge the gap between payday and unexpected expenses.</p>
          <p>TrueCred Loan Expert connects you with trusted micro lending platforms like KreditBee, MoneyTap, EarlySalary, Navi, and LazyPay that are RBI-registered and follow fair lending practices. Unlike informal borrowing from friends or unregulated lenders, micro loans from our partners come with transparent interest rates, clear repayment schedules, and zero hidden charges. Over 2 lakh customers have used micro loans through TrueCred for emergencies, bill payments, and short-term cash flow needs.</p>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">₹50K</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Loan Amount</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">1 Hour</span>
              <span class="info-label">Disbursal Time</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">100%</span>
              <span class="info-label">Digital Process</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Micro Loan Interest Rates — April 2026</h3>
          <table class="rate-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Bank / NBFC</th>
                <th>Interest Rate (p.a.)</th>
                <th>Processing Fee</th>
                <th>Max Tenure</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>KreditBee</td>
                <td>0% - 29.95% p.a.</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>12 Months</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>EarlySalary</td>
                <td>0% - 30% p.a.</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>12 Months</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>MoneyTap</td>
                <td>13% - 36% p.a.</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>12 Months</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Navi</td>
                <td>9.99% - 45% p.a.</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>12 Months</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>LazyPay</td>
                <td>15% - 33% p.a.</td>
                <td>Nil</td>
                <td>6 Months</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h3>Eligibility Criteria</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Indian citizen aged between 18 and 55 years</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum monthly income of ₹8,000 from any verifiable source</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Active bank account linked to mobile number</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Smartphone with internet for app-based application and e-KYC</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Valid Aadhaar and PAN card (PAN optional for loans under ₹10,000)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> No active default or overdue on existing micro loans</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>How to Get a Micro Loan</h3>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Download & Register</h4>
              <p>Register on TrueCred or our partner lending apps with your mobile number and basic details. Takes under 1 minute.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Verify Identity</h4>
              <p>Complete Aadhaar-based e-KYC with OTP. No physical documents needed. Your identity is verified in real-time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Get Instant Offer</h4>
              <p>See your approved loan amount and interest rate within 30 seconds. Choose the amount and tenure that suits you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Receive Money</h4>
              <p>Accept the offer and get money credited to your bank account within 10 minutes to 1 hour via UPI or IMPS.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Documents Required</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Aadhaar Card — for e-KYC via OTP (no physical copy needed)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> PAN Card — for loans above ₹10,000 (auto-verified digitally)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Bank Account — linked to your mobile for instant disbursal</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Selfie — live photo for face match verification</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> No income proof required for loans below ₹25,000 in most cases</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> No guarantor or collateral needed for any micro loan amount</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-file-signature"></i> Get Micro Loan Instantly</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Full Name" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="tel" class="form-input" placeholder="Mobile Number" maxlength="10" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input" required>
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Loan Amount</option>
                  <option value="3000">₹3,000</option>
                  <option value="5000">₹5,000</option>
                  <option value="10000">₹10,000</option>
                  <option value="15000">₹15,000</option>
                  <option value="20000">₹20,000</option>
                  <option value="30000">₹30,000</option>
                  <option value="40000">₹40,000</option>
                  <option value="50000">₹50,000</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="City" required>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-link"></i> Quick Links</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/business-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Business Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/home-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Home Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/loan-against-property"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Loan Against Property</a>
              <a href="/pages/gold-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Gold Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/education-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Education Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/car-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Car Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-cards"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Cards</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a>
              <a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Insurance</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Got Questions?</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Common questions about micro loans.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Is a micro loan safe? Are these apps legitimate?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              All micro lending partners on TrueCred are RBI-registered NBFCs or lending service providers operating under RBI-registered entities. They follow fair lending practices, transparent pricing, and data privacy guidelines. Always verify the lender's RBI registration on the RBI website before borrowing. Avoid apps not available on official app stores or those demanding upfront fees before disbursal — those are likely scams.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What can I use a micro loan for?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Micro loans can be used for any legitimate personal purpose: emergency medical bills, utility payments, grocery shopping, mobile recharge, rent shortfall, travel tickets, small appliance purchases, education fees, vehicle repairs, or bridging cash flow gaps between paydays. There are no end-use restrictions from the lender.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What happens if I cannot repay my micro loan on time?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              If you miss the repayment date, late payment charges (typically ₹200-500 per day or 1-2% per month on the overdue amount) will apply. Continued default will negatively impact your CIBIL score and may result in increased calls and reminders from the lender's collection team. It's always better to contact the lender before the due date to discuss extension or restructuring options rather than defaulting silently.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How many micro loans can I take at the same time?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              While there is no legal limit, most responsible lending platforms restrict you to 1-2 active micro loans at a time. Having multiple outstanding micro loans increases your debt burden and can lead to a debt trap. TrueCred recommends borrowing only what you can comfortably repay from your next salary. If you need a larger amount, consider a personal loan instead of multiple micro loans.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Do micro loans affect my CIBIL score?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, all RBI-registered lenders report micro loan data to credit bureaus. Timely repayment of micro loans positively builds your credit history, which helps you qualify for larger loans in the future at better rates. Conversely, defaults on micro loans will lower your CIBIL score. If you're new to credit, micro loans are actually a good way to start building your credit profile.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page CTA -->
  <section class="page-content" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-cta">
        <div>
          <h3>Need Cash Right Now? Get a Micro Loan</h3>
          <p>₹3,000 to ₹50,000 in your bank within 1 hour. 100% digital. No paperwork. Apply now.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:14px 32px;font-size:0.95rem;">
          Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
